# NoveraDB

Database module for the Novera.


Environment Variables
---------------------
NOVERA_DB_CONN_STR - Connection string for mongodb server (default: mongodb://user:pass@127.0.0.1:27017)
NOVERA_DB_DATABASE_NAME - Database name for the mongodb server (default: novera)
